# Reduce Docker build context size and improve build performance.
# (docker-compose.yml uses build context "." for every service)

# Build outputs
**/bin/
**/obj/

# Node
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.angular/

# Local tooling
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/

# Repo artifacts / publishes
artifacts/

# Test results / coverage
**/TestResults/
**/coverage/
**/coverage-report/

# Logs
**/*.log
